instincts.

08:10.990 --> 08:14.060 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, tell us
about Stephen
Bannon.

08:14.094 --> 08:15.862 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
