08:21.234 --> 08:26.272 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ROBERT COSTA: He's a colorful
and populist
figure on the American right,
someone who's

08:26.306 --> 08:31.745 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
