10:13.980 --> 10:18.985 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it is a sense that jobs
should stay here,
products should be made here,
foreign policy

10:19.018 --> 10:24.257 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
