back up.

32:01.086 --> 32:06.725 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNIFER GLASSE: A larger fleet
could mean
hundreds more jobs for deck
hands, engineers,

32:06.758 --> 32:13.832 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
