processing, buying and
selling fish.

32:13.865 --> 32:21.273 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Brixham Fish Market is already
the largest
on England's South Coast,
handling about $35

32:21.306 --> 32:23.275 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
million of annual trade.

32:23.308 --> 32:26.878 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
