33:02.480 --> 33:04.416 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And that was the fundamental
issue, really.

33:04.449 --> 33:09.321 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JENNIFER GLASSE: Robert
Simonetti exports
fish and serves it at a local
restaurant,

33:09.354 --> 33:12.657 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
