chips.

33:12.691 --> 33:16.328 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He doesn't think his out vote to
leave will
change much for his businesses.

33:16.361 --> 33:18.363 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ROBERT SIMONETTI, Fish Exporter:
For me, it
was all the immigration thing.

33:18.396 --> 33:20.165 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I think that's a big issue for
everybody.

33:20.198 --> 33:24.402 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You know, we want control about
who comes
into our country, really, the
people we don't

33:24.436 --> 33:26.204 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
