33:41.553 --> 33:44.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WENDY LANYON, Waitress: I do
believe we're
going to -- it's going to be
hard for us as

33:44.422 --> 33:49.427 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
