we had been
told it was going to be.

34:38.109 --> 34:41.913 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And it's just got worse and
worse.

34:41.947 --> 34:48.053 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNIFER GLASSE: And what do you
think Brexit
will do for Brixham and Devon
and Cornwall?

34:48.086 --> 34:54.693 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
EDGAR LAWRENCE: Depends very
much on the politicians.

34:54.726 --> 34:56.695 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
