34:56.728 --> 35:07.939 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Will they agree to everything we
want, which
Europe doesn't seem to want us
to have?

35:07.973 --> 35:13.011 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNIFER GLASSE: The picturesque
beaches of
Devon and Cornwall counties
attract tourists

35:13.044 --> 35:18.717 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that bring in revenue, but not
enough to keep
the local economies afloat.

35:18.750 --> 35:23.555 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
