government.

35:59.824 --> 36:03.428 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN POLLARD, Leader, Cornwall
Council: I
don't think the economic
argument played a

36:03.461 --> 36:05.497 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
