36:05.530 --> 36:09.334 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It was more on fear and a
dislike of Brussels.

36:09.367 --> 36:14.806 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
People like to blame somebody
for the ills
of the country, and Brussels was
getting the

36:14.839 --> 36:15.940 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
blame.

36:15.974 --> 36:18.943 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, it wasn't, in that sense,
economically
logical.

36:18.977 --> 36:21.646 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
