vote.

36:21.679 --> 36:27.585 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JENNIFER GLASSE: One of
Cornwall's poorest
areas is Redruth.

36:27.619 --> 36:30.989 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
