vote.

36:40.365 --> 36:44.269 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
VIKKI ROSTRON, Redruth,
Cornwall: I didn't
know enough about it to think
about it, to

36:44.302 --> 36:45.537 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
