do, you know?

36:50.708 --> 36:54.913 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNIFER GLASSE: The food bank's
founder says
the Brexit vote won't hurt
Cornwall because

36:54.946 --> 36:59.717 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
