38:42.687 --> 38:46.391 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For more on this, we turn to The
Washington
Post national security
correspondent Ellen

38:46.424 --> 38:48.193 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Nakashima, and Paul Vixie.

38:48.226 --> 38:51.496 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
