51:56.981 --> 52:02.119 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIKE GARCIA: We need to avoid
areas that look
shelly, indicating that the lava
has drained

52:02.152 --> 52:03.921 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
