52:03.954 --> 52:08.993 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So we try to look for places
where it looks
solid, so we can avoid
collapsing in on the

52:09.026 --> 52:09.994 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
