52:10.027 --> 52:11.028 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: I'm just going to
follow you.

52:11.061 --> 52:12.029 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
How's that?

52:12.062 --> 52:13.797 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MIKE GARCIA: Very good.

52:13.831 --> 52:18.569 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: But while we were
here, some
newly minted, still hot Hawaiian
earth melted

52:18.602 --> 52:21.638 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
