52:21.672 --> 52:23.974 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Wow, just like that.

52:24.008 --> 52:26.910 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Is the other one already gone?

52:26.944 --> 52:28.379 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MIKE GARCIA: No, no.

52:28.412 --> 52:29.847 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Oh, you're absolutely right.

52:29.880 --> 52:31.315 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Holy moly.

52:31.348 --> 52:33.050 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Wow.

52:33.083 --> 52:38.722 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
All in a day's work for an
intrepid geologist
determined to go with and to the
flow.

52:38.756 --> 52:41.458 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
